results.cleanName: Boundaries Crossed Theme Deck Ice Shock Black Kyurem

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
Feel the chill as Black Kyurem takes center stage in the electrifying Ice Shock theme deck! Foes have no time to stop and stare as Black Kyurem unleashes its electrifying Flash Freeze attack, and with Jellicents Stickiness Ability, they wont even be able to run and hide! The jolts continue as Lopunny takes time out from healing to drive the Defending Pokmon back to the Bench, helping Electivire blow your opponents fuses as it delivers punish attacks to Benched Pokmon. Can those who stand in your way avoid the blackout?

Contents for each Deck:
1 60-card pre-constructed deck
Damage counters
1 coin

Watch foes feel the heat as White Kyurem sets your game ablaze in the Cold Fire theme deck! Send opponents on a slipper downward spiral with Samurotts Destructive Whirlpool attack, and run rings around them as they try to fend off Darmanitans ferocious Damage Counterpunch attack. And, with Delibird, Delcatty, and Dunsparce delivering you deck-searching delights to drive the flames ever higher, your opponents will be going out...but not in a blaze of glory!

Contents for each Deck:
1 60-card pre-constructed deck
